CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1946 reads: "Eighth Wedding Anniversary - Mr. and Mrs. Nolan Williamson celebrated their eighth wedding anniversary and his birthday last week with a delightful celebration. Guests from Pittsburgh and New Kensington attended the affair which has held at their home, 6004 Houston Street. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Nolan Williamson, and Mrs. Williamson wearing corsage, celebrating eighth anniversary surrounded by men, women, and girl, behind table with three tiered cake, in Williamson home, 6004 Houston Street, another version
